      <title>野村证券因操纵债券交易，日本将暂停其参与债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-s-finance-ministry-to-suspend-nomura-from-debt-auctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在野村控股公司承认操纵债券期货市场后，日本财务省计划暂时禁止该公司参与政府债务拍卖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-s-finance-ministry-to-suspend-nomura-from-debt-auctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列计划回应伊朗袭击，油价有望周度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价小幅下跌，但仍有望连续第二周上涨，因为以色列准备好对伊朗实施报复计划，这增加了中东原油供应中断的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 23:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市下跌，焦点集中在政策简报上：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市下跌，表现不及亚洲其他股市，因为在周末的重要新闻发布会即将召开之际，投资者愈加谨慎，而该新闻发布会可能会为中国政府的财政刺激措施提供更多启示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
